OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA band of
OL,6,Fheavy rain in the west will cross
OL,7,Feastwards this evening, turning
OL,8,Fshowery overnight, the showers
OL,9,Fbecoming frequent and blustery. Gale
OL,10,Fforce winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FCloudy start with frequent
OL,13,Fblustery showers and gale force winds.
OL,14,FA brighter afternoon with some sunny
OL,15,Fintervals but still some showers.
OL,16,FWinds easing for a time before
OL,17,Fstrengthening overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
