OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FOvernight rain then blustery showers
OL,7,Fon Thursday, gales. Colder with
OL,8,Fsunshine and showers on Friday, snow
OL,9,Fon high ground. Remaining showery on
OL,10,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
